title: Peru's Castillo mulls cabinet reshuffle under pressure from opposition - Reuters
description: Peru's leftist President Pedro Castillo is mulling a cabinet reshuffle, a source told Reuters on Tuesday, less than a month after taking office and as he faces a critical confirmation vote later in the week by the opposition-led Congress.
